0. READ-ITEM ARRAY-SIZE TO N
1. MOVE N TO GAP
2. MOVE 0 TO SORTED
3. COMPARE SORTED WITH 1 IF EQUAL GOTO OPERATION 20
4. MULTIPLY GAP BY 10 GIVING TEMP
5. DIVIDE TEMP BY 13 GIVING GAP
6. COMPARE GAP WITH 1 IF LESS MOVE 1 TO GAP
7. COMPARE GAP WITH 1 IF EQUAL MOVE 1 TO SORTED
8. MOVE 1 TO I
9. COMPUTE LIMIT = N - GAP
10. COMPARE I WITH LIMIT IF GREATER GOTO OPERATION 3
11. COMPUTE J = I + GAP
12. READ ARR(I) INTO A
13. READ ARR(J) INTO B
14. COMPARE A WITH B IF NOT GREATER GOTO OPERATION 18
15. WRITE B TO ARR(I)
16. WRITE A TO ARR(J)
17. MOVE 0 TO SORTED
18. ADD 1 TO I
19. GOTO OPERATION 10
20. STOP
